import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['year'])]
    data = data.sort_values(by='year')
    plt.plot(data['year'], data['net_generation'], color='blue')
    plt.axhline(y=data['net_generation'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label='Mean')
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Net Generation')
    plt.title('What is the trend in net generation over the years?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.groupby(['source']).mean().reset_index()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.bar(data['source'], data['net_generation'], color='green')
    ax.set_xlabel('Source')
    ax.set_ylabel('Average Net Generation')
    ax.set_title('What is the average net generation by source?')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.tight_layout()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y')
    data = data.pivot_table(index='year', columns='source', values='net_generation')
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
    sns.heatmap(data, cmap='YlGnBu', annot=True, fmt='.2f', linewidths=.5)
    plt.title('What is the total net generation by year and source?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Source')
    plt.ylabel('Year')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
